{"tid":491724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[問卦] 香港人自在講廣東話，台灣人卻不能講台語","createTime":"2017-12-06T20:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T19:09:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d5bc2feb55fd22e999e244529eb6713032751f","tid":491724,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T20:25:59.000Z","msg":"時間Mon Oct 23 23:09:44 2017<br />\n<br />\n而且還有一點更奇怪，香港到處看得到粵語文句<br />\n各位看過港片字幕就知道，粵語和北京官話的用字不同<br />\n但是台灣就算講台語算蠻多的，但是台語用字幾乎沒有<br />\n去看看PTT的台語版，那才是真正的台語好嗎<br />\n只會講然後用一堆國語發音的字去亂湊根本是文盲<br />\n<br />\n光是八卦板常用的光是三字經的幹就要用姦才對<br />\n還有「三小」應該是「啥洨」，結果全部亂用一通<br />\n粵語對比台語來說，台語真的有很大進步空間"},{"pid":"f6c1237d97f0006dc2abf99e7725f2268491b499","tid":491724,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T20:34:04.000Z","msg":"推 wyverns: 不知道是不是誤會，但我記得粵語與客語、台語原本用字是 能通用的。都有音讀、文讀，破音字可以多到昏倒，這部份是小時看爺爺的手寫字典認識到的，這部份與粵語口語文字又不一樣，粵語口語文字應該也是之後發展出來，就跟台語卡拉OK文字差不多。都是為了讀音出版的。那近期的台語推 廣教育與這些舊台語又有點差距，大概是太拘泥考究而忽略了語言自己的生命。這部份也是推廣苦無成效的原因之一。<br />\n&rarr; wind0083: 這不是推不推廣的問題，是你自己愛不愛講需不需要的問題，大陸也是推廣普通話，但還是一堆四川話上海話廣東話在講 <br />\n<br />\n推 todao: 華北話笨來就不是絕大多數中國人的母語，中國人不講很正常 ，是台灣人被推廣國語推到不正常了。 加上外來政權不只強推還醜化閩客原母語，中國現在也把台灣這套拿來對粵語了。 所以久現在而言，推廣有助母語能見度沒錯，要推。<br />\n&rarr; enjoytbook: 一堆說台灣人有沒有的...那就是國民黨的成果 <br />\n&rarr; tiuseensii: 粵語文字也是很晚近才流行的。香港人華文粵讀很久了，台灣人從日治時期白話寫作有羅馬字和華語白話文之爭，白話漢字也一直不是主流 <br />\n&rarr; todao: 人家那叫書面語，誰跟你華文粵讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且人家近年已經有在討論書面語應該用粵語文法來寫了好嗎"},{"pid":"eddeb9377294b97406b129b42cd38555e05dd95a","tid":491724,"uid":22675,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T20:37:18.000Z","msg":"粵語，有自己的文字系統，一般人看到香港網友打的文章，肯定看不懂，感覺就很勁。 台語，有人說台語也有自己的文字，但很多人用的台語文字都是錯誤的， 像凍蒜就是錯誤的台語用法，那請告訴我正確的當選的台語字該怎麼打？ 很少人可以用正確的台語文字寫出一篇文章，但香港人卻可以用粵語文字寫出來， 為何台語文字這麼弱？ 粵語，講話時幾乎都是全程粵語，完全不需要參雜國語。 台語，有些時候一個句子裡，還是要參雜國語才能講得下去，無法全程100%用台語講完。 香港人講粵語是不搭配國語的，但台灣人講台語，好像有時候一定要搭配國語才行， 為何台語這麼弱？ 粵語，電影、音樂、戲劇、明星，很多人在用，像周潤發、周星馳、劉德華、黎明、 張學友、張國榮、陳奕迅、謝霆鋒，等等。 台語，台語的發展就沒有粵語那麼強，為什麼？ 粵語，台語，兩個很像，但仔細看卻又有很大差異的語言，為何發展差這麼多？"},{"pid":"9ba98462f5591b98f9fbdc20c29e81a9acde017b","tid":491724,"uid":104443,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T20:37:44.000Z","msg":"揭後語都係粵語一大特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\neg,) 阿荗整餅，冇嗰樣整嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5725c35bd0c0373fa05fe318dd92c7fe71d00436","tid":491724,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T20:38:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1508771387.A.A77.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1508771387.A.A77.html&d=%2Bspj0IWIdMouqG%2Fhzemmd5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f1846715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1508771387.A.A77.html</a>"},{"pid":"8cc309b13ca31dc3a80dc0db1b312ce0e5e54200","tid":491724,"uid":104443,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T20:40:30.000Z","msg":"其實箇中原因唔難想像，香港受百幾年英國殖民統治，間接保護度清末嘅文化直到宜家"},{"pid":"4b24d7742029da417abddbfd0b164843f5a28ac6","tid":491724,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T20:53:08.000Z","msg":"照計台語既文字系統係應該參照番文言文<br />\n當然我好懷疑而家後生一代既台灣人仲識唔識台語<br />\n講黎講去得果幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515113642c0fe16b08ccc06ee1e59bdaa565943e","tid":491724,"uid":37136,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照計台語既文字系統係應該參照番文言文<br />\n當然我好懷疑而家後生一代既台灣人仲識唔識台語<br />\n講黎講去得果幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n後生果代直程同大陸接左軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5455d9f659db14f05537795bf4e0d26c79f4a32f","tid":491724,"uid":8187,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:09:05.000Z","msg":"香港人講廣東話<br />\n其實中間咪又係夾雜好多英文"},{"pid":"0b3c91f08392a3bb2b97cc2b88a458db928a0a12","tid":491724,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照計台語既文字系統係應該參照番文言文<br />\n當然我好懷疑而家後生一代既台灣人仲識唔識台語<br />\n講黎講去得果幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大部份都識既，可以用台語溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係果邊識台語同上一代既人傾生意特別吃香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc382e310953538bdac8bf566670e4b8753b76d5","tid":491724,"uid":65773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:14:23.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"80fd2c04b3805b9d02611b6dd695558415b3de3a","tid":491724,"uid":2373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:15:28.000Z","msg":"唔識台語，最多都係識講句「話格LE趕」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係感覺台語好垃圾，記得之前捷運小巨蛋站譯唔到台語點讀，搞到要讀三次小巨蛋國語，好戇尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n粤語唔會有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22d716e7f0cac42e5cc5bda3c1f2bcf190fb028","tid":491724,"uid":2373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:18:07.000Z","msg":"仲有「𨑨迌」我知呢個係台語嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e745dd54a3752166680c174363a0877293f91eae","tid":491724,"uid":189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:18:14.000Z","msg":"宜家先知原來台語有字讀唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c87081e8116c1c836eb284b5bf0c8e01168756e","tid":491724,"uid":127804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:53:03.000Z","msg":"其實好多人都唔識寫返廣東話既正字<br />\n更加無學過粵拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9886bf3f3e5ccc7cd85defbba4b57d1ab5598a","tid":491724,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:56:49.000Z","msg":"國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac786698114e57ad69fb72642ac14b912b32ad1","tid":491724,"uid":80567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T23:13:31.000Z","msg":"國共時走難去嘅 好多都唔識講<br />\n再加上當時國黨要「反攻大陸」 所以學「國語」「國文」<br />\n台語自自然然流失通用性<br />\n<br />\n如今後生仔同後生仔講野都係講國語<br />\n只得D生鬼既台語詞彙好似潮語咁流傳落去<br />\n<br />\n另外相比台語，台灣原住民語言瀕危得多<br />\n台語起碼同福建話同源 最多死左個台灣口音<br />\n不過由台灣文化睇 的確係一大損失"},{"pid":"f247c8f661cb0ad803956a0cfa4b635bff765635","tid":491724,"uid":22313,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T23:26:02.000Z","msg":"因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請講中文</span></span>"},{"pid":"838e16f86ce95866077a2731f13ba1b2519f00c6","tid":491724,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T00:02:00.000Z","msg":"49年撤台國民黨大部份係北方人<br />\n在國民黨強迫中原北方文化統治30,40年<br />\n嚴禁在軍公教等地方講台語<br />\n強推北京話滅台語<br />\n鼓吹中原文化<br />\n<br />\n另外現在民進黨建議<br />\n將英文列為第2官方語言<br />\n但有一班人走出來反對"},{"pid":"d34647a77111dddc07121826eefc90bf0704b313","tid":491724,"uid":84275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T00:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人講廣東話<br />\n其實中間咪又係夾雜好多英文</blockquote><br />\n因為大英「祖國」嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2247a2cd5373028d60530f846afea2a42d210ef2","tid":491724,"uid":59898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T00:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請講中文</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台狗大陸狗"},{"pid":"4540717aec9da38e3f68a235a0a514cdeda4dc93","tid":491724,"uid":53105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-0