80ce1f71f13b42f247ec3e75e8c614918ee22c","tid":491724,"uid":44070,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:34:22.000Z","msg":"之前打機同過一個台仔傾過計，佢話台中同台南都經常講台語，只係台北比較少。不過台語喺台灣既廣泛性同常用性都慢慢遞減，特別係台北"},{"pid":"a4def692e620eadd9b4fc2e3117806b57daf0f7e","tid":491724,"uid":55792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:41:08.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦，用台語黎同廣東話比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ead91cb7a000065647dd9db932ac3d8d49972d3","tid":491724,"uid":3594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實好多人都唔識寫返廣東話既正字<br />\n更加無學過粵拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪on9㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廣東話都有自己一套拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫粵拼<br />\n係同普通話完全唔同<br />\n但唔係好普及 通常中文系個d 先會教"},{"pid":"6064a13443ddadfc6535081b8e7ac8a00f8dc799","tid":491724,"uid":109173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:13:05.000Z","msg":"點解要拎黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本粵語都好少人寫到全部正字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b56543f48604c36656c326b042b843c1bf4a924","tid":491724,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要拎黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本粵語都好少人寫到全部正字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同音就係正字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033f53c1235674706a17b46b43038b87e43dcd6a","tid":491724,"uid":24730,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"好彩七十年代出咗許氏兄弟同黎彼得，否則廣東話會一路沒落"},{"pid":"da45d0ad4f466dcd8a6c5fec94f2b5a135d32ae7","tid":491724,"uid":21028,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"其實唔關事 因為粤語有不斷做字 <br />\n嘅咗嘢閪閂啲哋嚟喺嗰㗎嘛喎(多數連接或助語詞)<br />\n<br />\n以前睇過一d文字演化 語言可以話係人類第二次進化 而文字係會有生死既 <br />\n例如有啲字 常用字 罕用字 <br />\n雫(已被日字化 粤音 no5) 磡(呢個字香港心熟悉 但其實冇其他字串連成詞) 幵 (姓氏) 鑫 犇 淼 焱 惢 垚 畾 (森詞多 冇死到 同埋音同樣 森 讀*心* 所以以上果d唔會讀個字砌出黎既音 森都唔讀木啦 姦字都係)<br />\n只可以講 語文不斷發展 有d字 佢地讀唔出 都要作 不過本身粤語發音小則九 多則十二 就算叫鬼佬台灣佬都學唔到 粤語算係最難既一個語言體系"},{"pid":"835c826267bee7443308ffa1231dd41d2d10b594","tid":491724,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩七十年代出咗許氏兄弟同黎彼得，否則廣東話會一路沒落</blockquote><br />\n又未必 只係廣東歌成為新market 為咗殖民時代上基層有娛樂 英殖民多年 行文談吐都用英文 都冇被磨滅粤語 佢非小眾語體<br />\n本身唐代語言較接近粤 而粤差d成為國語 粤語唔係你所想 咁小眾語言"},{"pid":"a1830a47e5d9c2169a6bd4218a89ad6a17487841","tid":491724,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實好多人都唔識寫返廣東話既正字<br />\n更加無學過粵拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪on9㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廣東話都有自己一套拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫粵拼<br />\n係同普通話完全唔同<br />\n但唔係好普及 通常中文系個d 先會教</blockquote><br />\n所以香港英文係唔教拼音 <br />\n其實粤語教拼音 中文同音字教讀法 而香港都造咗套拼音方便有學過既人"},{"pid":"75aef1e9ea427731a6cf1022d25d32b3612a40d3","tid":491724,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己放棄唔保護，冇得怪人。<br />\n台灣啲中文真係好垃圾，成日都有啲「作一個乜乜的動作」，當自己日文啊？愈長愈有禮貌啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日文的確影響好深<br />\n係台語方言化既環境下有時佢地自己都自己都未搞清講緊某特定詞係台語定日文"},{"pid":"995eb2a857bff0810bcbdce077d1045cfada0dc5","tid":491724,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己放棄唔保護，冇得怪人。<br />\n台灣啲中文真係好垃圾，成日都有啲「作一個乜乜的動作」，當自己日文啊？愈長愈有禮貌啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日文的確影響好深<br />\n係台語方言化既環境下有時佢地自己都自己都未搞清講緊某特定詞係台語定日文</blockquote><br />\n始終日統治過 佢既文化融合唔講得笑 你睇泡菜就知 會有敬語 (我諗日文先最多 但自己思考下 中文都唔多 作為中原隔離 以前受中文影響多 唔會有呢d)"},{"pid":"e16ec1127f32d2ae040f421dd81ec47b560b618f","tid":491724,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:28:47.000Z","msg":"台狗特別on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486c21932e407a614c0a9d1df11e5d913b019e3e","tid":491724,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"個人覺得 台語好撚難聽"},{"pid":"cc32f05311257388b86b46c66e17ce68dd5ab756","tid":491724,"uid":72667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"唔撚講咁鳩多<br />\n<br />\n保衛粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c050b4693241dbd3b78f058e8964b9d533f3f569","tid":491724,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次打機見到台狗，同佢地講看不懂你說什麼，請打台語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個提議唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc08729e9c53ed046e66890370cf9084158e56db","tid":491724,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚講咁鳩多<br />\n<br />\n保衛粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維護嶺南文化<br />\n維護香港文化<br />\n反對推普廢粵"},{"pid":"628437813f2d6a88ecc4d1675075237ad90ee27f","tid":491724,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照計台語既文字系統係應該參照番文言文<br />\n當然我好懷疑而家後生一代既台灣人仲識唔識台語<br />\n講黎講去得果幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全台灣閩南話講得最好嘅可能係中國國民黨台南市議員謝龍介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9097bb646e657b9c8814eb6c1ad64e38f45920","tid":491724,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>照計台語既文字系統係應該參照番文言文<br />\n當然我好懷疑而家後生一代既台灣人仲識唔識台語<br />\n講黎講去得果幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全台灣閩南話講得最好嘅可能係中國國民黨台南市議員謝龍介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n謝龍介真係咩場合都會用台語<br />\n亦唔會就人地用國語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反民進黨識台語無咩幾個可以講得流利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54028511e6735b10f07453b00390a408fc031a26","tid":491724,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"有時打機 <br />\n發現台狗打字成日打同音字就算<br />\n睇死人"},{"pid":"68c72d66a86d7b7e0c4b800e29a6d72b308577eb","tid":491724,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"台灣30歲打上個班個個識講，有啲廢中廢老仲唔識國語<br />\n不過後生就危險啲好多識聽講就唔流利"},{"pid":"ba4ff78626c25bc6015757e04535ceb0830b07fe","tid":491724,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識台語，最多都係識講句「話格LE趕」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係感覺台語好垃圾，記得之前捷運小巨蛋站譯唔到台語點讀，搞到要讀三次小巨蛋國語，好戇尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n粤語唔會有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為閩南話本身唔用「蛋」嚟稱呼雞蛋 係用「卵」"},{"pid":"f950dda179e91aaea0bf84aca47b4f16ce3fc433","tid":491724,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實箇中原因唔難想像，香港受百幾年英國殖民統治，間接保護度清末嘅文化直到宜家</blockquote><br />\n你肯定唔清楚英格蘭以前點打壓威爾斯語"}]}